1. Policy application (σ π−→σ′) corresponds to a field update governed by dissipative operators L and sparse intervention vectors uπ generated by the policy. The update also includes semantic drag (λ), which resists policy changes, and entropy injection from inference steps (κ). This represents semantic inference as energy descent with sparse forcing.

