10. **28S rDNA copy number and levels**: The research evaluates 28S rDNA copy numbers using monochrome multiplex quantitative PCR (MMQPCR) in post-treated muscle tissue. No significant alterations were detected, ensuring that the ICE system does not affect overall rDNA content or rRNA levels.

11. **Validation of the ICE mouse**: The study confirms the proper functioning of the ICE system through Western blot analysis of tissues from tamoxifen-treated mice, detecting I-PpoI expression and gH2AX activation in various organs.

