**October 29:**
In a fantastical post, Nate introduced the 'Standard Galactic Alphabet (SGA),' a unique writing system featured in the Commander Keen video game series. The SGA is a simple substitution cipher where each Latin alphabet letter corresponds to a distinct symbol, primarily utilized for English text within the games.

**October 31:**
