The uniﬁed action is a scalar functional that encapsulates the dynamics of both the AQDP (Asymptotic Quantum Desynchronization Process) deformation of spacetime and the RSVP (Relativistic Semantic Vectors and Principles) deformation of semantic geometry. This action is designed to treat uncertainties in the physical metric and uncertainties in the semantic metric on an equal footing, as both forms of uncertainty manifest as aﬃne deformation of the connection.

